9. Editorial Review

This source should be treated as a gateway text: accessible, devotional, practical, and broad. It is ideal for introducing kundalini without drowning the reader in technical tantra.

Editorial danger: making it sound like a medieval tantric root-text. It is not. It is a modern yogic synthesis.

Best editorial angle:

Sivananda turns kundalini into a disciplined path of purification, concentration, and God-realization. Energy is not spectacle; it is the soul’s hidden verticality becoming conscious.

