13. Imaginarium Use

For the Path of Re-Rendering, Sivananda’s Kundalini Yoga is useful as the energetic purification model.

Ordinary consciousness is rendered through scattered prāṇa, desire, habit, and identification. Kundalini Yoga re-renders the person by:

gathering dispersed energy
purifying the body-mind vessel
converting sensation into attention
converting attention into ascent
converting ascent into union
converting union into realization

The core Imaginarium thesis:

The human being is not merely a thinking subject inside a body. The body itself is a vertical symbolic instrument, and consciousness can be re-rendered by purifying, concentrating, and awakening the forces latent within it.

